Clock DesktApp is a desktop application designed for Windows 8.1, Windows 10 and macOS Sierra which provides time, date and day information about different time zones. 
With Clock DesktApp you can:
•	Display specific time for a place or a time zone by adding a clock.
•	Add multiple clocks (10 clocks at most) and customize each of them.
•	Display time in analog or digital format depending on your preference.
•	Display time in digital format as 24-Hour or 12-Hour AM/PM. 
•	Display day and date in different formats according to your preference.
•	Display the phase of the moon.
